  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "Valmet M78 7.62x51毫米轻机枪",
      "en": "Valmet M78 7.62x51 light machine gun"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "M78",
      "en": "M78"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "Valmet M78是芬兰AK步枪的RPK风格重枪管班组支援武器型号。它最初是为芬兰军队开发的M74骑兵机枪，但从未被采用。如果被采用，它将使用7.62x39毫米口径。为了出口，该公司提供了该口径以及5.56x45毫米和7.62x51毫米口径。这一实验性设计将成为商业出口型M78的基础。由于这些武器是在1986年之前进口的，将其制造成可转让的机枪是合法的。-伊恩·麦科勒姆",
      "en": "The Valmet M78 is the RPK-style heavy barreled squad support weapon pattern of the Finnish AK. It was initially developed as the M74 cavalry machine gun for Finnish military service, but never adopted. If it had, it would have been chambered for 7.62x39mm. For export, the company offered that caliber as well as 5.56x45mm and 7.62x51mm. That experimental design would serve as the basis for the commercial export M78. Because these were imported before 1986, it was legal to manufacture them into transferrable machine guns. -Ian McCollum"
    },
